tn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781630/extras/827d51a6ad8ae47bad3c7a3f4419c21c.avif?t=1549059205\" width=350 height=139 /></span><br><br><strong>3 pickups: </strong><br>Boost your character for a competitive edge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781630/extras/9521e1bb2ef0b6c0feffa254cd03eb66.avif?t=1549059205\" width=375 height=181 /></span><br><br><strong>Controller support: </strong><br>Hook up any combination of DualShock 4, Xbox One, Steam Link or other third-party controllers and get going, fast.",
